An accident between a minibus taxi and a SUV occurred at 13:00 on the Schoemanskloof Road between Poplar Creek and Montrose. Solange Soares, TRAC spokesperson, confirmed the accident. ALSO READ: Barberton community demands “divorce” from Mbombela City Soares said that 11 people were injured and no fatalities have been reported so far. Lowvelder will update as more details become available.